Maintainer: Lukas Sablica <lsablica@wu.ac.at>
Description: Estimation scheme offers objects for flexmix package together with the necessary M-steps 
             for both of the distributions.
             The random sampling scheme of the package offers two random number generators for the
             Poisson Kernel-Based Distribution (PKBD) and one generator for spherical Cauchy 
             distribution on the sphere.
